{"tid":837284,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"英雄聯盟世界賽》主題曲曝光？傳BLACKPINK將獻唱","createTime":"2018-09-26T09:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T15:11:35.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ab001ee962ff5f080c1fa3a47932e6fc46f33e72","tid":837284,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/145/5bab27349aa61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F145%2F5bab27349aa61.jpg&h=74ec29b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著《英雄聯盟》世界大賽腳步越來越近，今（26）日官方公布了新的主題曲名稱〈RISE〉，有北美網友爆料與知名電競記者推測，新主題曲很有可能是由YG娛樂大勢女團「BLACKPINK」演唱！  <br />\n<br />\n「BLACKPINK in your area！」喜歡韓國流行樂的粉絲肯定對於這句歌詞耳熟能詳，隨著《英雄聯盟》世界大賽腳步越來越近，新的主題曲也成了玩家關注的焦點，今（26）日官方公布了新的主題曲名稱為〈RISE〉，有北美網友爆料與知名電競記者推測，新主題曲很有可能是由YG娛樂大勢女團「BLACKPINK」演唱！<br />\n<br />\n今日凌晨，Riot Games於官網上悄悄地更新了許多世界賽的相關訊息，其中包含歷屆的世界賽主題曲，今年的主題曲曲名〈RISE〉也隨之曝光，根據公布時程來看，明日將會公布相關訊息，加上有四個全新以「偶像」為主題女性英雄造型曝光，其中包含阿璃、阿卡莉、凱莎與伊芙琳，這樣的巧合也使得網友議論紛紛，猜測這是否與主題曲相關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/145/5bab2f252e77b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F145%2F5bab2f252e77b.jpg&h=d1de42bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有四個全新以「偶像」為主題女性英雄造型曝光，其中包含阿璃、阿卡莉、凱莎與伊芙琳，這樣的巧合也使得網友議論紛紛<br />\n<br />\nESPN知名記者「Fionn」Tyler  Erzberger更在推特上大膽推測：「今年世界賽主題曲叫作〈RISE〉，BLACKPINK的歌基本上都是大寫字母，嗯...這代表什麼呢？」但他也先打預防針，表示這僅是他個人基於曲名、造型數量與BLACKPINK的行程表來推算的，所以一切都只是猜測。<br />\n<img src=\"http://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/145/5bab302627630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F145%2F5bab302627630.jpg&h=ebe02548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nESPN知名記者「Fionn」Tyler Erzberger在推特上大膽推測本次主題曲演唱團體為BLACKPINK<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6512e687d89fd04abc3a6a6fdbc8709b77a2af9","tid":837284,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43130d137e16c726c5c0b8d92cc0d0386e9cdd17","tid":837284,"uid":92465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"jisoo b💕"},{"pid":"e22ea7ec950668f9b1cc5642ae1ad8dc4e25fab0","tid":837284,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"riot寧願請BP都唔請我哋T寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec479ffef81e265885ff5b501e6ef0f535d9ff4b","tid":837284,"uid":140454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"諗起舊年啲歌首首都好似串緊Faker咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca39bc40620f06887424a08e4f4f06370113e66d","tid":837284,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e22ea7ec950668f9b1cc5642ae1ad8dc4e25fab0","tid":837284,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"riot寧願請BP都唔請我哋T寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"我敢寫包單我地兔瓦斯行GIRL CRUSH會&gt;包皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039c4632c6a46a84a1048c558a1c988691e4f072","tid":837284,"uid":135767,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c212915aea711c4b76d221fbfd6ff023b7805dd6","tid":837284,"uid":70274,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid"